    "faq_bradJb": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_RrLqCK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Power Sculpt",
            "answer": "<p>Using advanced electromagnetic technology, this non-invasive treatment delivers powerful muscle contractions to tone, lift and define key areas of your body. Simultaneously builds lean muscle and improves fat metabolism for a sculpted, refined result.</p>",
            "show_embedded_section": true,
            "embedded_image": "shopify://shop_images/MAR-PWS-TRTAREAS1-INSTAST-REV01_pws_stories_treatment_areas_1.jpg",
            "embedded_layout": "image_content",
            "embedded_layout_mobile": "image_content",
            "embedded_layout_gap": 40,
            "embedded_layout_gap_mobile": 20,
            "embedded_image_ratio": "portrait",
            "embedded_image_ratio_mobile": "portrait",
            "embedded_step_1": "Step 1",
            "embedded_step_1_title": "How It Works",
            "embedded_step_1_text": "<p>Power Sculpt uses focused electromagnetic energy to stimulate thousands of powerful muscle contractions in your chosen treatment area.</p><p>These contractions force the muscle fibres to adapt, strengthen, and grow while also enhancing fat metabolism in the surrounding tissue.</p><p>In short: it tones, tightens, and burns simultaneously.</p>",
            "embedded_step_2": "Step 2",
            "embedded_step_2_title": "Treatment",
            "embedded_step_2_text": "<p>During treatment, you’ll feel strong, rhythmic muscle contractions - not pain, as the electromagnetic energy engages the muscles.<br/><br/>There’s no downtime or soreness; you can return to normal activities immediately. Most clients even describe the feeling as an intense workout without breaking a sweat.</p>",
            "embedded_step_3": "Step 3",
            "embedded_step_3_title": "After",
            "embedded_step_3_text": "<p>After your Power Sculpt session, you can return to normal activities immediately - there’s no downtime or recovery required. You may feel a mild muscle ache similar to an intense workout, but this simply means your body is already responding and strengthening.</p>",
            "embedded_step_4": "",
            "embedded_step_4_title": "",
            "embedded_step_4_text": ""
          }
        },
        "question_DLzrmg": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Carbon Facial",
            "answer": "<p>Using advanced electromagnetic technology, this non-invasive treatment delivers powerful muscle contractions to tone, lift and define key areas of your body. Simultaneously builds lean muscle and improves fat metabolism for a sculpted, refined result.</p>",
            "show_embedded_section": true,
            "embedded_image": "shopify://shop_images/CLF-3.jpg",
            "embedded_layout": "image_content",
            "embedded_layout_mobile": "image_content",
            "embedded_layout_gap": 40,
            "embedded_layout_gap_mobile": 20,
            "embedded_image_ratio": "portrait",
            "embedded_image_ratio_mobile": "portrait",
            "embedded_step_1": "1",
            "embedded_step_1_title": "Cleaning And Applying",
            "embedded_step_1_text": "<p>The skin is cleansed and a thin layer of medical-grade liquid carbon is applied.<br/><br/>The carbon acts as a powerful absorber, drawing out impurities, oil, and dead skin cells from deep within the pores.</p>",
            "embedded_step_2": "02",
            "embedded_step_2_title": "Laser Activation",
            "embedded_step_2_text": "<p>Once the carbon has penetrated the skin, a specialised laser is passed over the area.<br/><br/>The laser light is absorbed by the carbon particles, gently vaporising them along with trapped debris, bacteria, and dead skin cells.<br/><br/>This process provides deep exfoliation and pore purification while stimulating collagen production in the underlying skin layers.</p>",
            "embedded_step_3": "03",
            "embedded_step_3_title": "Cooling And Hydration",
            "embedded_step_3_text": "<p>After the laser treatment, the skin is cooled and hydrated with soothing serums to restore balance and comfort.<br/><br/>Your skin will look instantly clearer and smoother with a noticeable glow that continues to improve over the following days.<br/><br/>For lasting results, a course of 4 to 6 sessions spaced a few weeks apart is recommended.</p>",
            "embedded_step_4": "",
            "embedded_step_4_title": "",
            "embedded_step_4_text": ""
          }
        },
        "question_3WxPfa": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Red Light Therapy",
            "answer": "<p>Using advanced electromagnetic technology, this non-invasive treatment delivers powerful muscle contractions to tone, lift and define key areas of your body. Simultaneously builds lean muscle and improves fat metabolism for a sculpted, refined result.</p>",
            "show_embedded_section": true,
            "embedded_image": "shopify://shop_images/WhatsApp_Image_2025-11-08_at_22.29.00_65d5d3de.jpg",
            "embedded_layout": "image_content",
            "embedded_layout_mobile": "image_content",
            "embedded_layout_gap": 40,
            "embedded_layout_gap_mobile": 20,
            "embedded_image_ratio": "portrait",
            "embedded_image_ratio_mobile": "portrait",
            "embedded_step_1": "01",
            "embedded_step_1_title": "Cleansed And Prepared",
            "embedded_step_1_text": "<p>The skin is gently cleansed to ensure maximum light absorption.<br/><br/>This preparation ensures your session is safe, effective, and tailored to your skin’s needs.</p>",
            "embedded_step_2": "02",
            "embedded_step_2_title": "Celluma LED Therapy Session",
            "embedded_step_2_text": "<p>You will relax comfortably as the Celluma device is positioned above the treatment area.<br/><br/>The panel emits targeted red and near-infrared light wavelengths that penetrate deep into the skin to energise cells and trigger collagen renewal.<br/><br/>The session lasts around 20 to 30 minutes and is completely painless. Most clients describe it as warm, calming, and deeply relaxing.</p>",
            "embedded_step_3": "03",
            "embedded_step_3_title": "Recovery And Maintenance",
            "embedded_step_3_text": "<p>After your session, your skin will appear instantly refreshed with a healthy, natural glow.<br/><br/>There is no downtime, and you can return to normal activities straight away.</p>",
            "embedded_step_4": "",
            "embedded_step_4_title": "",
            "embedded_step_4_text": ""
          }
        }
